bac5c47a8a44c5","tid":396421,"uid":37869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你地呢班人同以前啲人屌鳩話地球係圓個人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界好多野都未知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一味就係唔信 乜都話on9<br />\n而家唔係要你100%信足<br />\n之前啲post都係討論下姐<br />\n咁咪大家一齊探討下啲未知既野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n「地球係球體」有可證偽性：你楂飛機去地面既盡頭發現真係一片虛無，就可以證明地球唔係球體<br />\n<br />\n「歷史被不明來歷份子改寫導致部份人記憶與記錄不符」（又稱曼德拉效應）無可證偽性：你證明唔到佢係假，換句說話講就係佢講撚哂<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我地而家笑鳩你係同當年笑鳩地圓說既人有好撚大既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n究竟有幾多人覺得自己係天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917e2d9cd99cf88b7ce2313bdb4f72759d3329e9","tid":396421,"uid":5929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"唔信唔信囉 信咪信 洗唔洗專登開個post話人"},{"pid":"9bc860eea01791df111f70ebcd60e2096edbf9fc","tid":396421,"uid":683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔信唔信囉 信咪信 洗唔洗專登開個post話人</blockquote><br />\n咁關你撚事呀 洗唔洗轉登comment話樓主"},{"pid":"8cc8d132c628617cb9848595fc53ce2c66fe7f91","tid":396421,"uid":42407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔信唔信囉 信咪信 洗唔洗專登開個post話人</blockquote><br />\n乜都唔比講，你仲惡過共產黨"},{"pid":"4ab9ce2ca16c137c85df23092b451e08e1f3bfca","tid":396421,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee60b9d64e13839bbbb41a036a73e41d09cc3a27","tid":396421,"uid":70527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:39:45.000Z","msg":"KitKat 真係記得有一橫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm